videoSnippet.title: Alpha Zero's "Immortal Zugzwang Game" against Stockfish
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Read more about Deep Mind Alpha Zero here https://arxiv.org/pdf/1712.01815.pdf

Link to the other games https://lichess.org/study/wxrovYNH

A chess game between Deep Mind Alpha Zero and Stockfish

Google Deep Mind Alpha Zero vs Stockfish
One of the games
